cred$ClasSalariosMinimos <- cut(cred$SalariosMinimos, c(0,2,4,Inf),
                                labels = c("[0-2] SMLMV",
                                           "(2-4] SMLMV",
                                           ">4 SMLMV"),
                                include.lowest = TRUE)

Suma de los modos de cr√©dito

cred$modosCred <- apply(subset(cred,select=c(Amigos:Prenderia)),1,sum)

Modos de cr√©dito por g√©nero y si son profesionales

require(lattice)
## Loading required package: lattice
opciones <- simpleTheme(pch = 19, col = "blue")
xyplot(modosCred ~ Profesional|Genero, data=cred,
       par.settings = opciones)

xyplot(jitter(modosCred) ~ Profesional|Genero, data=cred,
       par.settings = opciones)

bwplot(modosCred ~ Profesional|Genero, data=cred,
       par.settings = opciones, notch = TRUE)
